<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ạ̉yhạ ạlậb ạlgẖny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā ạảyũhā ạlậbu ạl̊gẖanī̃̊ .. fī ạb̊nika qadi ạkẖ̊tar̊tanā
 ạảḥ̊bab̊tanā mun̊dẖu ạlạảzal̊ .. wafīhi qad̊ bārak̊tanā

[V2]
 2- ạản̊ta ạảbūnā ʿizũnā .. wanaḥ̊nu ạảẘlạduⁿ laka
 biạb̊nika tabanãẙtanā .. limad̊ḥi maj̊di faḍ̊lika

[V3]
 3- wabihi qad̊ ṣāra lanā .. bika ạl̊tiṣāquⁿ lilạảbad̊
 wabihi qad̊ ạảs̊ʿad̊tanā .. yā ạảyũhā ạlậbu ạlṣãmad̊

[V4]
 4- bihi lanā kulũ ạl̊ḥubūr̊ .. bihi ạlẓãlāmu ṣāra nūr̊
 ại̹nãhu yan̊būʿu ạlsũrūr̊ .. lanā ại̹lay̱ dah̊ri ạldũhūr̊</lyrics>
</song>